data.text:
NDC 70518-1040

Sertraline

Sertraline

Sertraline is a Oral Tablet, Film Coated in the Human Prescription Drug category. It is labeled and distributed by Remedyrepack Inc.. The primary component is Sertraline Hydrochloride.
